  <brief_title>Sunitinib + Docetaxel as Second-line Treatment in Gastric Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Phase II Trial of Sunitinib and Docetaxel in Advanced Gastric Cancer Patients Who Had Prior Chemotherapy With Fluoropyrimidine and Platinum</official_title>
