  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether Sunitinib and Docetaxel is effective in the
      treatment of advanced gastric cancer patients who had prior chemotherapy with
      fluoropyrimidine and platinum.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This is a randomized phase II trial of Sunitinib and Docetaxel in advanced gastric cancer
      patients who had prior chemotherapy with Fluoropyrimidine and Platinum.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
